title: Charming One Bedroom includes Utilities
neighborhood: Arlington in town on the hill
posting_body: This darling cottage is set serenely and privately below the quiet street above it.
You'll love that it has it's own yard space and a huge patio!
You can relax in the shade or enjoy sunbathing, either one!
Comfortable and large living room is the heart of this home.
The bedroom and living rooms both have ample storage closets.
The vintage character and spacious bathroom features a brand new vanity, mirror and fixtures and a ton of linen/bath storage and counter space.
Sunny garden beds are yours to grow flowers, fruits or veggies!
Easy budgeting here with your water, sewer, garbage and electricity included in your rent.
Enjoy Arlington's small town charms here and the easy parking that is always available right out front of your home!
This property requires proof of identity and ability to pay (adequate income).
This property does not accept reusable credit/background checks.
